            "id": "ch01-rat-page-2",
            "slug": "rat-page-2",
            "title": "RAT: Reading Test — Page 2",
            "content": "## Remember Questions\r\n\r\n**1. According to Chapter 1, what is the book's central learning arc, in order?**\r\n\r\nA. Decisions -> Analytics -> Queries -> Relationships -> Tables -> Data\r\n\r\nB. Data -> Queries -> Tables -> Relationships -> Analytics -> Decisions\r\n\r\nC. Data -> Tables -> Relationships -> Queries -> Analytics -> Decisions\r\n\r\nD. Tables -> Data -> Relationships -> Analytics -> Queries -> Decisions\r\n\r\n**2. Which two recurring projects does the book use across chapters?**\r\n\r\nA. The Grading Database and the PetVax Veterinary Hospital Database\r\n\r\nB. The Grading Database and the Coffee Shop Database\r\n\r\nC. The PetVax Veterinary Hospital Database and the Hospital Billing Database\r\n\r\nD. The Northwind Database and the Grading Database\r\n\r\n**3. Which tool does Chapter 1 describe as turning cleaned and queried data into dashboards and reports for decision-makers?**\r\n\r\nA. SQLite\r\n\r\nB. Microsoft Access\r\n\r\nC. Power BI\r\n\r\nD. Google Forms\r\n\r\n**4. Which chapter section guides students through the Grading Database one step at a time?**\r\n\r\nA. Core Concepts\r\n\r\nB. Let's Build\r\n\r\nC. Terms Treasury\r\n\r\nD. Lab\r\n\r\n**5. Which Bloom level does Chapter 1 associate with designing a new structure, query, report, dashboard, or recommendation?**\r\n\r\nA. Remember\r\n\r\nB. Apply\r\n\r\nC. Evaluate\r\n\r\nD. Create\r\n\r\n**6. Select ALL that apply: According to Chapter 1, which of the following are listed as the book's core competencies?**\r\n\r\nA. Foundational information literacy\r\n\r\nB. Applied database management\r\n\r\nC. Cloud network administration\r\n\r\nD. Data integrity and system quality\r\n\r\nE. Strategic problem solving\r\n\r\n**7. Select ALL that apply: Which of the following are named in Chapter 1's table of tools and environments?**\r\n\r\nA. Microsoft Access\r\n\r\nB. Supabase / PostgreSQL\r\n\r\nC. Oracle Forms\r\n\r\nD. Power BI\r\n\r\nE. BigQuery\r\n\r\n**8. Which chapter range does Chapter 1 place in Part 6: Strategy and Integration?**\r\n\r\nA. Chapters 1-3\r\n\r\nB. Chapters 4-5\r\n\r\nC. Chapters 11-14\r\n\r\nD. Chapters 15-17",
