    "id": "ch02-rat-page-2",
    "slug": "rat-page-2",
    "title": "RAT: Reading Test — Page 2",
    "content": "## Remember Questions\r\n\r\n**1. In the DIKW hierarchy, what level answers \"What was recorded?\"**\r\n\r\nA. Information\r\n\r\nB. Knowledge\r\n\r\nC. Data\r\n\r\nD. Wisdom\r\n\r\n**2. Which component of the five-component framework refers to the physical devices a system uses?**\r\n\r\nA. Software\r\n\r\nB. Hardware\r\n\r\nC. Data\r\n\r\nD. Processes\r\n\r\n**3. According to the chapter, what does the \"R\" in the R.E.A.D. framework stand for?**\r\n\r\nA. Reporting and Review\r\n\r\nB. Representation and Retrieval\r\n\r\nC. Recording and Recall\r\n\r\nD. Retrieval and Response\r\n\r\n**4. Select ALL that apply: Which of the following are data quality dimensions discussed in the chapter?**\r\n\r\nA. Accuracy\r\n\r\nB. Timeliness\r\n\r\nC. Popularity\r\n\r\nD. Consistency\r\n\r\nE. Completeness\r\n\r\n**5. In the Input-Process-Output model, what are the resources that enter the organization called?**\r\n\r\nA. Outputs\r\n\r\nB. Processes\r\n\r\nC. Inputs\r\n\r\nD. Feedback\r\n\r\n**6. What term does the chapter use for the people and groups affected by an organization's actions?**\r\n\r\nA. Managers\r\n\r\nB. Stakeholders\r\n\r\nC. Customers\r\n\r\nD. Employees\r\n\r\n**7. Select ALL that apply: Which of the following are stages in the DIKW hierarchy?**\r\n\r\nA. Data\r\n\r\nB. Information\r\n\r\nC. Analysis\r\n\r\nD. Knowledge\r\n\r\nE. Wisdom\r\n\r\n**8. According to the chapter, what does BITM stand for?**\r\n\r\nA. Business Information and Technology Methods\r\n\r\nB. Business Intelligence and Technical Management\r\n\r\nC. Business Information Technology Management\r\n\r\nD. Broad Information and Technology Modeling",
    "pageNumber": 2,
    "totalPages": 7,
    "chapterId": "ch02",
